Message.En:
I reported this to the temple as well, 
but I'll let you know here too. 
I saw <LQEM> 
by the river near the village. 
If they attack the village, 
it will be a disaster. 
I'll protect the village, so could someone nearby 
hunt down about <LQVA> of them?
Message.Jp:
ミスリウ森林には遺跡や洞窟なんかも結構あるが、そういう所は<LQEM>なんかの巣になることも多い
あいつらは群れると厄介だ。もし腕に覚えがあるなら、<LQVA>匹程度仕留めてくれ。報酬も多少は出すとも
